  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个导出文件的状态流转图。用户提交请求后，系统会先进入requested状态，然后自动转到processing处理中，处理完成变成completed，最后文件有过期机制，变成expired结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "requested",
        "processing",
        "completed",
        "expired",
        "export_file"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这是一个线性流程：requested → processing → completed → expried，最后结束。我注意到completed之后直接到expired，这个过期是自动触发的还是用户下载后才计时？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "completed",
        "expired"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是时间触发的，文件生成后保留7天，无论用户是否下载都会过期。另外起点和终点要用标准起始符，图标题就叫\"Stati export_file\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "title",
        "expired"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先用stateDiagram-v2来画，标题设置好，从起始节点连到REQUESTED，然后依次连接PROCESSING、COMPLETED、EXPIRED，最后回到终止节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stateDiagram-v2",
        "title",
        "[*]",
        "REQUESTED",
        "PROCESSING",
        "COMPLETED",
        "EXPIRED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我看看... 状态名都用大写没问题，但流程上我想确认一下：processing到completed是自动流转吗？还是需要加个判断？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PROCESSING",
        "COMPLETED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "目前我画的是直接流转。如果处理失败的话，我们是不是需要个失败分支？比如processing可以走到failed？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PROCESSING",
        "failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "先不用加失败分支，这个版本保持简单。不过我发现你刚才说的\"expried\"拼错了，应该是\"expired\"，i和r的位置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "expired"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，修正为EXPIRED。现在图已经完整了：从起始点到REQUESTED，经过PROCESSING、COMPLETED，最后EXPIRED回到终止节点，标题是\"Stati export_file\"。",
